settings.html: The Dell Precision 7865 workstation tower is a high-performance, reliable, and efficient solution for demanding workloads. Meticulously designed to meet the needs of professionals, the Precision 7865 features robust processing power, capable graphics performance, and specialized features to enhance productivity and deliver optimal results. Whether you're a radiologist working with complex medical images, an engineer designing innovative products, or a creator producing cutting-edge content, the Dell Precision 7865 workstation tower is the ideal tool for your success.

settings.title: Unparalleled Performance
settings.content:
Experience uncompromising performance with the Dell Precision 7865 workstation tower, powered by up to 64 cores of AMD Ryzen Threadripper PRO processors.

Radiologists can rely on the Precision 7865 to handle the most demanding radiological workflows with ease, enabling them to deliver precise and timely medical diagnoses with confidence. The workstation's powerful processors also support seamless multitasking, allowing radiologists to work on multiple tasks simultaneously without any slowdown.

settings.title: High-Precision Imaging Graphics Solutions
settings.content:
Unlock the full potential of your workflow with the Dell Precision 7865 workstation tower's support for up to two 300W graphics cards.

Choose from a comprehensive selection of professional AMD W series, NVIDIA RTX graphics, and Barco MXRT graphic cards, each meticulously engineered to deliver exceptional performance for the most demanding radiological tasks, such as complex image analysis, developing and training AI-powered applications, and multitasking across multiple demanding imaging workflows.

With the Precision 7865's dual-graphics capabilities, you can experience accelerated performance and achieve optimal results, empowering you to deliver the best possible care to your patients.

settings.title: Customization Options
settings.content:
The Dell Precision 7865 workstation tower is a powerful and versatile machine that can be used for a variety of demanding workloads, including radiology. It is powered by the latest AMD Ryzen Threadripper PRO processors, which offer up to 64 cores and 280W of TDP. This makes the Precision 7865 ideal for tasks such as complex image analysis, developing and training AI-powered applications, and multitasking across multiple demanding imaging workflows. In addition to its powerful processing and graphics capabilities, the Precision 7865 also offers up to 56TB of storage, RAID capabilities, and self-encrypting options. This makes it ideal for storing and protecting large datasets of medical images.

The Precision 7865 also comes with a variety of other features that make it ideal for radiologists, including:

  • 8x DDR4 RDIMM up to 1TB at 3200MHz for fast memory performance
  • 1350W 80 Plus high efficiency PSU for reliable power delivery
  • High speed I/O including optional Thunderboltâ„¢ 3 for connecting to high-performance peripherals

The Dell Precision 7865 workstation tower is the perfect solution for radiologists who need a powerful, versatile, and reliable machine to handle the most demanding workloads.

settings.title: Powerful Processors for Radiological Excellence
settings.content: Empower your radiological endeavors with the Dell Precision 7865 workstation, featuring up to 64-core AMD Ryzen Threadripper PRO processors for unparalleled performance. Tailored for the most demanding radiological tasks, this workstation ensures precision and timeliness in diagnoses. Radiologists can confidently navigate complex medical imaging datasets and AI-powered applications, thanks to the robust processing capabilities of the Precision 7865. Its powerful processors support seamless multitasking, enabling radiologists to efficiently handle multiple tasks simultaneously without slowdown. With top-tier performance and multitasking efficiency, the Dell Precision 7865 workstation is a reliable companion for radiological professionals, enhancing their ability to deliver accurate and timely results with confidence in critical medical scenarios.

settings.title: High-Velocity DDR4 ECC Memory
settings.content: Harnessing the power of high-speed DDR4 ECC memory, the Dell Precision 7865 workstation offers abundant RAM for seamless management of data-intensive medical imaging tasks. Elevate performance further by scaling up to 1TB of 3200MHz DDR4 memory, ensuring an expansive and efficient workspace. The rapid memory speed not only mitigates delays but also significantly enhances overall productivity, catering to the demands of professionals engaged in intricate medical diagnostics. This workstation is finely tuned to provide optimal efficiency, allowing users to navigate through extensive datasets with ease. Additionally, the efficient use of power aligns with sustainable practices, making the Dell Precision 7865 a robust and eco-conscious solution for critical medical imaging workflows.

settings.title: Effortless Mobility and Connectivity: Unveiling the Dell Precision 5860 Workstation Advantages
settings.content: Enhance your portability with integrated carrying handles, making it effortless to transport your workstation. Experience rapid network speeds for data activities like uploading, downloading, and streaming with 1G and 10G native speeds. Connect all your essential devices seamlessly with a range of USB-A and USB-C ports. Enjoy easy manageability and security with AMD Advanced Management featuring DASH, streamlining the process of overseeing and safeguarding your workstation. This feature-rich Dell workstation not only prioritizes convenience in transportation but also offers swift connectivity and efficient device management, ensuring a comprehensive and user-friendly experience for professionals on the move.

settings.title: Elevate Radiology with Dell Precision 7865 Workstation
settings.content:
The Dell Precision 7865 workstation tower is a powerful machine that can help you create fully-immersive VR content. This can be used for pre-surgical planning, image analysis, and patient education.

The Precision 7865 is also certified by a wide range of independent software vendors, so you can be sure that it can run the latest and most demanding radiological applications without any problems.

Radiologists can use the latest AI-powered Precision Data Science Workstations to optimize their devices for the applications they use most, empowering them to get their most important work done faster.

settings.title: Reliability You Can Trust
settings.content: Reliability is the cornerstone of the Dell Precision 7865 Tower Desktop Workstation, especially tailored to meet the intricate demands of radiologists. Engineered with precision and rigorously tested, this workstation is built to endure the challenges of your profession. Dell's distinguished reputation for reliability transcends to this specialized workstation, ensuring it remains a steadfast partner throughout your career as a radiologist, supporting you in delivering accurate and timely diagnoses with unwavering confidence.
